NK071(du)006:0: ldem dgongs brgyad kyi lhan thabs bzhugs so //
NK071(du)006:2: khyad par dgongs pa can gyi mdo'i don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)006:7: zhugs pa ldem po dgongs pa dang //
NK071(du)006:8: mtshan nyid ldem po dgongs pa dang //
NK071(du)006:9: gnyen po ldem po dgongs pa dang //
NK071(du)006:10: brgyur ba ldem po dgongs pa'o //
NK071(du)006:11: nyan thos dang ni ngo bo nyid //
NK071(du)006:12: de bzhin nyes pa 'dul ba dang //
NK071(du)006:13: brjod pa zab pa nyid dang ni //
NK071(du)006:14: ldem po dgongs pa 'di rnam bzhi //
NK071(du)006:17: zhugs pa la ldem por dgongs pa dang /
NK071(du)006:18: mtshan nyid la ldem por dgongs pa dang /
NK071(du)006:22: nyan thos la sogs pa theg chen la zhugs pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)006:23: phyi rol gyi gzugs sogs la don yod par gsungs pa ste /
NK071(du)006:25: gzugs char snang ba tsam la dgongs la sgra ji bzhin par go yang /
NK071(du)006:26: de dag gi blo dang mthun pa'i sgo nas /
NK071(du)006:27: rim gyis theg chen la 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod de /
NK071(du)006:29: gzugs sogs yod par bstan pa ni //
NK071(du)006:30: des ni 'dul ba'i skye bo la //
NK071(du)006:31: dgongs pa'i dbang gi gsungs pa ste //
NK071(du)006:32: bardzusa te skye ba'i sems can bzhin //
NK071(du)006:35: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo med pa la sogs pa bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)006:37: kun brtags la snang ba'i ngo bo nyid kyis mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK071(du)006:38: gzhan dbang la skyes pa'i ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK071(du)006:39: yongs grub la don dam pa'i ngo bo nyid med pa'o //
NK071(du)006:40: dgongs pa ni bden zhen ldog pa ste /
NK071(du)006:42: ngo bo nyid ni rnam gsum las //
NK071(du)006:43: ngo bo nyid med rnam gsum gyis //
NK071(du)006:44: dgongs nas chos rnams thams cad kyi //
NK071(du)006:45: ngo bo nyid med bstan pa yin //
NK071(du)006:48: sgrib pa brgyad kyi nyes pa 'dul ba'i phyir theg chen bstan pa ste /
NK071(du)006:49: sgrib pa brgyad kyi dang po sangs rgyas thub pa nyid la brnyas pa'i sgrib pa'i gnyen po ni /
NK071(du)006:50: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs kyi che ba mang du gsungs
NK071(du)006:51: nas nga nyid de'i tshe sangs rgyas rnam gzigs su
NK071(du)006:54: cung zad tsam gyis chog par 'dzin pa'i gnyen po ni /
NK071(du)006:55: bcom ldan 'das kyis la lar sbyin pa la sogs pa smad la /
NK071(du)006:57: lnga pa gdams ngag gi gzugs dang stobs la sogs pa nga rgyal gyi gnyen po ni /
NK071(du)006:58: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku la sogs pa phun sum
NK071(du)006:59: tshogs pa'i khyad par lhag par basngagasa pa lta bu'o
NK071(du)006:60: // drug pa khams gsum gyi phun sum tshogs pa la chags pa 'dod chags kyi gnyen po ni /
NK071(du)006:61: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su dag pa'i yon tan la basngagasa pa brjod pa lta bu'o //
NK071(du)006:62: bdun pa dge ba la mi sbyor ba'i gnyen po ni /
NK071(du)006:63: sems can gang zhig sngar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' la gnod pa byas na /
NK071(du)006:64: phyis de dag yon tan can du shes te /
NK071(du)006:65: 'gyod pa 'ba' zhig skye ba la dgongs nas /
NK071(du)006:66: sangs rgyas byang sems la gnod pa byas pa de
NK071(du)006:67: dag thams cad ni mtho ris su skye bar 'gyur
NK071(du)006:70: las dang po pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ma nges pa'i rigs can 'ga' zhig la /
NK071(du)006:71: grogs po ngan pa dang 'phrad pa la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)006:72: rkyen gyis theg chung du ldog pa'i gnyen por dam
NK071(du)006:73: chos pad+ma dkar po la sogs par theg pa 'di
NK071(du)006:74: kho na ste zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK071(du)006:75: nyan thos chen po rnams sangs rgyas pa lung bstan to //
NK071(du)006:76: de ltar sgrib pa brgyad kyi gnyen por theg chen bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)006:79: snying po med la snying por shes //
NK071(du)006:80: phyin ci log la legs par gnas //
NK071(du)006:81: nyon mongs pas ni rab nyon mongs //
NK071(du)006:82: byang chub dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK071(du)006:85: sems rnam par g.yeng ba ni 'khor ba'i snying po yin la /
NK071(du)006:86: de med pa ni snying po ste gtsang bar 'dzin pa dang /
NK071(du)006:89: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i phyin ci log gi lta ba de dag mi gtsang ba dang /
NK071(du)006:90: sdug bsngal ba la sogs par rtogs pa'i don mi mnyams pa'i sgo nas legs par gnas pa dang /
NK071(du)006:91: yun ring por gzhan gyi dka' spyad la ngal bas /
NK071(du)006:92: lus sems nyon mongs par byed pa zhig gis byang chub thob par 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)006:93: yang ni pha ma gnyis ni gsad bya zhing /
NK071(du)006:94: bram ze gtsang ma gnyis bzung la sogs pa'o //
NK071(du)006:96: sangs rgyas kyi gsungs pa'i chos rnams ni rtogs sla'o //
NK071(du)006:97: snyams nas brnyas pa spang ba'o //
NK071(du)006:100: mnyam pa nyid dang don gzhan dang //
NK071(du)006:101: de bzhin du ni dus gzhan dang //
NK071(du)006:102: gdams ngag gis ni bsam pa la //
NK071(du)006:103: dgongs pa rnam pa bzhir shes bya //
NK071(du)006:106: dang po mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa ni /
NK071(du)006:107: sh+aakya thub pas sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs kyi basngagasa pa brjod nas /
NK071(du)006:108: nga nyid de'i dus sangs rgyas rnam gzigs su gyur to //
NK071(du)006:109: zhes gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK071(du)006:111: chos sku mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa'o //
NK071(du)006:113: thub pa la brnyas pa'i nyes pa spang bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)006:114: gnyis pa don gzhan la dgongs pa ni /
NK071(du)006:115: chos nyid snang ba'i ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK071(du)006:116: ma skyes pa la sogs pa sngar mtshan nyid ldem pa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar ro //
NK071(du)006:117: gsum pa dus gzhan la dgongs pa ni /
NK071(du)006:118: gang zag bde ba can du smon lam 'debs pa de dag der skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)006:119: zhes gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK071(du)006:121: dus ring por zhig na de ltar 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)006:122: dgos pa ni le lo'i gnyen por 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)006:124: gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa ni /
NK071(du)006:125: sems can 'ga' zhig la sbyin pa basngagasa shing /
NK071(du)006:128: dge ba mi byed pa la ltos te /
NK071(du)006:130: tshul khrims la sogs pa la ltos na dman pa'o //
NK071(du)006:132: kha cig sbyin pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK071(du)006:133: des chog par 'dzin pa rnams gong ma la sbyor ba'o //
NK071(du)006:135: ldem dgongs kyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)006:136: dgongs pa bzhi ni gnyen po la ldem por dgongs par 'dus so //
NK071(du)006:137: 'o na ci'i phyir dgongs pa dang ldem dgongs su bzhag ce na /
NK071(du)006:138: dgongs pa bzhi dang dgos ched bzhi gtso bor bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)006:139: ldem dgongs brgyad kyi lhan thabs zhes bya ba /
NK071(du)006:140: bshes gnyen rnams kyis bskul ngor btsun pa nam mkha' dpal gyis sbyar ba'o ////
